1
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:20,200
Just treat the patient.

2
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:22,000
Why are you touching each other?

3
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:26,280
You misunderstand.

4
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:29,000
I was just instinctively trying to catch that poisonous bug,

5
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,860
and he was afraid it would hurt me.

6
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:37,880
Chuyun,

7
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,880
seems to be reacting.

8
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,160
Master Du,

9
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:43,970
it seems our treatment method is really working.

10
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:47,220
What's with all this "us" and "them"?

11
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:50,720
I can help you too.

12
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,800
Master Shen,

13
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:54,080
you are a martial artist.

14
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:56,039
You probably won't understand any of this,

15
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:57,560
so it's better not to force it.

16
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,560
Are you mocking me for being clumsy?

17
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,120
I

18
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,840
mean no such thing.

19
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:05,760
He probably means you don't understand medicine,

20
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:08,360
and you might end up hurting yourself instead.

21
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,600
If I don't understand, just teach me.

22
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:11,800
I learn very quickly.

23
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,400
But medicine isn't something

24
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,880
you can master overnight.

25
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:20,920
Jiu...

26
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,020
What are you doing?

27
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:28,520
I just suddenly remembered,

28
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:30,560
"Thinking of My Brothers on the Ninth of September".

29
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:33,320
I wanted to ask about this "brother".

30
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:38,920
What riddles are you speaking in?

31
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:43,600
Ji Bai, Divine Physician Ji, Great Divine Physician Ji.

32
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,200
After you teach me,

33
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:48,400
wouldn't it be better to have one more healer in the world?

34
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:51,280
But I...

35
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,920
Master Duyu knows about poisonous insects.

36
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,980
Just let him take care of Lady Chuyun.

37
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:57,120
It's time for your consultation.

38
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,520
Hurry and take me to the clinic to save lives.

39
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,720
Everyone is waiting.

40
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,520
I'll trouble you then.

41
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,320
Okay.

42
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,120
It's my duty.

43
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,240
Once I've settled Miss Chuyun in,

44
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,640
I'll come find you.

45
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,960
So, for this herb,

46
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,640
you must remember to dry it.

47
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,200
Otherwise, it'll get moldy,

48
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,400
and lose its potency.

49
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:18,220
Physician Ji, your patient has arrived.

50
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:20,360
Master Du,

51
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:23,160
could you please teach him to identify the herbs?

52
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:24,640
I'll go check on the patient.

53
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:26,040
Don't worry. No problem.

54
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:28,020
I'll teach him everything I know.

55
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,040
I'm going.

56
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:50,000
Brother Shen.

57
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,520
Don't bother.

58
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,200
I can learn it myself.

59
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:56,460
You're too polite, Brother Shen.

60
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,680
Since you're determined to learn,

61
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,200
I'll definitely teach you.

62
00:03:59,200 --> 00:03:59,920
Besides,

63
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,880
it's Miracle Doctor Ji's wish,

64
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,640
and my honor.

65
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:09,560
Brother Shen.

66
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,280
Shen, look.

67
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,320
This is ginseng.

68
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:20,320
As for ginseng, it is bitter, slightly sweet, and warm.

69
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:23,120
It targets the spleen, lungs, heart, and kidneys.

70
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:24,920
It tastes bitter and slightly sweet.

71
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:29,320
Slightly bitter but not draining, it replenishes Qi and strengthens the body.

72
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:36,770
So this is what ginseng looks like.

73
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,640
Shen.

74
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:43,960
It seems you're not interested in medicinal herbs.

75
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,060
I'm not interested in you.

76
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,280
If you say that, Shen,

77
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:55,080
and Miss Ji finds out,

78
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:57,920
I'm afraid she'll be disappointed and sad.

79
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,640
Ji Bai is already betrothed.

80
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,720
I hope you know that.

81
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:04,200
Shen.

82
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:06,560
Feelings cannot be forced.

83
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,240
Miss Ji's feelings

84
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,680
are not something you or I can control.

85
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:14,080
The fact that Miss Ji came to Sitai Town alone

86
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:17,640
shows she has no feelings for her betrothed.

87
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:21,320
About Miss Ji and her betrothed,

88
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,640
how would an outsider like you know?

89
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:27,120
Aren't you an outsider too, Shen?

90
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,520
I've been through life and death with her.

91
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:32,520
Naturally, I'm different from you.

92
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,600
How enviable.

93
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:39,520
But regarding your past with Miss Ji,

94
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,159
I don't want to ask too much.

95
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:42,400
I only hope

96
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:45,680
you can respect Miss Ji's choice,

97
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:48,440
and not cause her trouble.

98
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:53,040
Of course I won't cause her trouble.

99
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,120
Shen.

100
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:58,800
It seems you have designs on her.

101
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,120
Give me your hand.

102
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:06,020
Don't be afraid. I'll apply the medicine first.

103
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,260
Did you insert the needle?

104
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,120
Not yet.

105
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,320
I have to apply the medicine first.

106
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:19,280
I have to wait for the herbs to absorb,

107
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:21,320
before I can use the needle.

108
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,840
Done. The needle is in.

109
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,760
That fast?

110
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:32,960
I didn't feel a thing.

111
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:35,820
Does your stomach still hurt?

112
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:41,280
Mother, my stomach doesn't hurt anymore.

113
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:44,440
Thank you, Doctor.

114
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,560
Quick, thank the Doctor.

115
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,000
Don't let yourself get cold when you go back.

116
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,840
Soak your feet in hot water often.

117
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,880
You're having inappropriate thoughts.

118
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:52,760
What nonsense are you talking about?

119
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,000
I...

120
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,530
What are you arguing about?

121
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:57,720
I heard you arguing from far away.

122
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,440
I...

123
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,970
I don't want him to teach me.

124
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:01,840
Why?

125
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,240
I am sorry.

126
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,280
My knowledge is too shallow.

127
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,970
I cannot teach Master Shen.

128
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,760
I know your capabilities.

129
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:14,120
Is it because you aren't studying hard?

130
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:18,380
Forget it, I'll teach you myself.

131
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,160
Let's go.

132
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:22,720
Okay, let's go.

133
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:31,960
Childish.

134
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:07,120
What are you doing?

135
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,120
Here.

136
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:18,840
For coughing blood, use Chebula fruit,

137
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:21,440
add pumice, gardenia, and snakegourd.

138
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:24,040
Indigo clears the liver and cools the blood.

139
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:27,000
Take this to cure coughing up phlegm and blood.

140
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:28,160
Not bad.

141
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:30,720
You've mastered the Soup Rhyme.

142
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:33,840
You also understand the basic acupuncture points.

143
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:41,280
Then shouldn't you give me a reward, Master?

144
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,400
Sure.

145
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,290
What reward do you want?

146
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,520
Stop seeing Duyu in private,

147
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:51,240
okay?

148
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:54,960
I have no personal relationship with him.

149
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:57,490
We were just discussing Chuyun's condition.

150
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:59,840
Chuyun is improving.

151
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,640
She can perceive light now.

152
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:04,960
I want to cure her eyes completely soon.

153
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,410
Anyway, my intuition tells me,

154
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,100
he is not a good person.

155
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:15,480
Why are you so hostile towards Master Du?

156
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,680
Why is that?

157
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,080
I am not.

158
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:20,920
I just don't think he's trustworthy.

159
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:44,200
The residual poison is gone. You can leave.

160
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:45,400
No.

161
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:48,440
I haven't learned any real skills from you yet.

162
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,370
I'm not leaving.

163
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:54,320
Mastering real skills takes decades.

164
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:56,320
Don't you want to roam the world?

165
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,920
If I learn medicine from you,

166
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:03,880
it'll be useful when I roam the world later.

167
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:04,840
Right?

168
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,560
In that case,

169
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:11,480
you may stay.

170
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:16,700
Master, please have some tea.

171
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:21,690
I wonder if my master received the letter.

172
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:23,880
If there's a chance,

173
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:26,330
I'd like to introduce you to my master.

174
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:27,920
She is the one

175
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:29,280
who has the real skills.

176
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:32,860
Divine Doctor Ji, Young Master Shen.

177
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:36,520
Miss Hu,

178
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,600
what brings you here?

179
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,520
You saved my father at the medical hall last time.

180
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:42,240
I came specifically to thank you.

181
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,970
There is no need to be so polite.

182
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:46,040
How is your father's condition?

183
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:49,120
Divine Doctor Ji, my father is much better.

184
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:50,560
Thank you for your concern.

185
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:52,560
I came to repay your kindness.

186
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:55,880
I made some pastries for you to taste.

187
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:01,960
Thank you for your kindness, Miss.

188
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,720
We will enjoy them.

189
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:08,700
Young Master Shen.

190
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,760
Actually, I have another reason for coming.

191
00:12:12,760 --> 00:12:14,420
You saved my father last time.

192
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:16,120
I am truly grateful.

193
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:19,280
I...

194
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:21,400
I have a bold request.

195
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:31,760
Mr. Shen, I...

196
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,720
I want to offer myself to you

197
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,160
to repay your kindness.

198
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:37,640
I know this may sound sudden,

199
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,440
but I am sincere.

200
00:12:52,520 --> 00:12:54,640
Miss Hu, I am already betrothed.

201
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:57,680
I'm afraid I cannot accept your kindness.

202
00:12:57,680 --> 00:12:58,560
I know.

203
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:01,540
You and Physician Ji look like a perfect couple.

204
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:04,730
But I am willing to be a concubine to take care of you both.

205
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:10,920
There is nothing between us.

206
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:49,760
Yi Yinan.

207
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:50,680
Xiao Xiaoxue, Yi Yinan.

208
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:50,680
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

209
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:52,210
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen.

210
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:18,960
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

211
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:19,960
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

212
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,170
Pan Xiulong.

213
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:24,640
Sun Zhang, Zhang Chong.

214
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:25,120
Lu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

215
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:25,120
Pan Xiulong.

216
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:25,600
Lu, Sun, Zhang.
